@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qndxcg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.85) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.79)) / ((v0 + 0.50 + v2 + 0.34) - (tmp + 0.51 - v1 + 0.62)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(v1))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = wp.cos((v0 - 0.04))
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.59 * v2 + 0.88) - (v1 + 0.22 * v1 + 0.48)) / (tmp * v1))
    data[tid] = v0
